OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FPartly
OL,6,Fcloudy this evening with any remaining
OL,7,Fheavy showers soon clearing away. The
OL,8,Frest of the night will then be largely
OL,9,Fcloudy with the risk of a few showers
OL,10,Flater.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FA mainly dry morning.
OL,13,FTurning overcast with outbreaks of
OL,14,Frain during the afternoon. Freshening
OL,15,Fwinds, occasionally strong later in
OL,16,Fthe north.
OL,17,
OL,18,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,19,FMainly dry, bright and breezy during
OL,20,Fthis period. Some sunny spells,
OL,21,Fperhaps a few showers at times.
